      <description>&lt;main class="wp-block-group is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow"&gt; &lt;div class="wp-block-group is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained"&gt;&lt;h1 class="wp-block-post-title"&gt;Kusuriya no Hitorigoto&amp;nbsp;(WN)&lt;/h1&gt;   &lt;div style="height:1px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;   &lt;/div&gt;   &lt;div class="entry-content wp-block-post-content is-layout-constrained wp-block-post-content-is-layout-constrained"&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://ncode.syosetu.com/n9636x/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"&gt;By Hyuuga Natsu&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;figure class="wp-block-image alignright"&gt;&lt;img width="207" height="299" src="https://shikarito.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/91x1yhj7gil.jpg" alt="91x1Yhj7GiL" class="wp-image-259" sizes="(max-width: 207px) 100vw, 207px" /&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;    &lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="has-text-align-center"&gt;LN ver. LICENCED BY J-NOVEL CLUB&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;She was captured by hunters for palace ladies for the inner palace when she went out to gather medicinal herbs.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;As a result, Maomao, a pharmacist from the pleasure district, is now working in a refined place. While displeased with the current situation, she thought she could work quietly until the end of her service, but her curiosity and knowledge wouldn&amp;#8217;t allow that.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;With her solving of an unexpected incident, she caught the eyes of the emperor’s favoured consort and a eunuch.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Even today, Maomao, who wants to quickly return to town, sighs with a laundry basket in hand.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" /&gt;    &lt;p class="has-text-align-center"&gt;&lt;em&gt;Table of Contents&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;h2 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-center"&gt;Arcs 1 &amp;#8211; 11 are no longer available here.&lt;/h2&gt;    &lt;h3 class="wp-block-heading"&gt;Arc 10: &lt;strong&gt;The Western Capital 2&lt;/strong&gt; (≈LN12)&lt;/h3&gt;    &lt;p class="has-text-align-center"&gt;[1- 27] &lt;a href="https://knhtranslations.wordpress.com/"&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="has-text-align-center"&gt;&lt;a href="https://shikarito.wordpress.com/kusuriya-no-hitorigoto/10-28-family-head-and-successor/"&gt;28&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="https://shikarito.wordpress.com/kusuriya-no-hitorigoto/10-29-a-sense-of-dread/"&gt;29&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="https://shikarito.wordpress.com/kusuriya-no-hitorigoto/10-30-chue/"&gt;30&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="https://shikarito.wordpress.com/kusuriya-no-hitorigoto/10-31-successor/"&gt;31&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="https://shikarito.wordpress.com/kusuriya-no-hitorigoto/10-32-a-good-sleep/"&gt;32&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="https://shikarito.wordpress.com/kusuriya-no-hitorigoto/10-33-compromise/"&gt;33&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="https://shikarito.wordpress.com/kusuriya-no-hitorigoto/10-34-growth/"&gt;34&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="https://shikarito.wordpress.com/kusuriya-no-hitorigoto/10-35-your-name/"&gt;35&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;h3 class="wp-block-heading"&gt;Arc 11: &lt;strong&gt;Daily Life&lt;/strong&gt; (≈LN13)&lt;/h3&gt;    &lt;p class="has-text-align-center"&gt;No longer available&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;h3 class="wp-block-heading"&gt;Arc 12: &lt;strong&gt;Kada&lt;/strong&gt; (≈LN14)&lt;/h3&gt;    &lt;p class="has-text-align-center"&gt;&lt;a href="https://shikarito.wordpress.com/kusuriya-no-hitorigoto/12-01-the-juniors/"&gt;1&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="https://shikarito.wordpress.com/kusuriya-no-hitorigoto/12-02-factional-dispute/"&gt;2&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="https://shikarito.wordpress.com/kusuriya-no-hitorigoto/12-03-endless-bothers/"&gt;3&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="https://shikarito.wordpress.com/kusuriya-no-hitorigoto/12-04-the-person-yo-seeks/"&gt;4&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="https://shikarito.wordpress.com/kusuriya-no-hitorigoto/12-05-the-village-settlement/"&gt;5&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="https://shikarito.wordpress.com/